    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036940/extras/250304f856950f91c507cb9b8c098ccd.poster.avif?t=1761030131\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036940/extras/250304f856950f91c507cb9b8c098ccd.webm?t=1761030131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036940/extras/250304f856950f91c507cb9b8c098ccd.mp4?t=1761030131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在一次灾难性的太空探险后，你成为了塔尔沃斯(Tarvos)——一个未知且未被探索的卫星上唯一的幸存宇航员。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">起初看似宜居的环境很快揭示了其真正的梦魇般本质。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036940/extras/7a4ff871f516a2489ce6954161417cdb.avif?t=1761030131\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036940/extras/65f2c75d97cc43b7e8e109dc75d45653.poster.avif?t=1761030131\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036940/extras/65f2c75d97cc43b7e8e109dc75d45653.webm?t=1761030131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036940/extras/65f2c75d97cc43b7e8e109dc75d45653.mp4?t=1761030131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的目标是生存在塔尔沃斯充满敌意的表面上，并揭开可能帮助你逃离的秘密。你需要面对成群的怪物，探索神秘的地点，并找到通往废弃实验室的路，这里可能藏着答案……以及你回家的唯一机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036940/extras/0049ee59df3c17364a20b556a292d282.avif?t=1761030131\" width=616 height=100 /></span><strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036940/extras/7f729f6ffa3fd33bc936abb47690cd92.poster.avif?t=1761030131\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036940/extras/7f729f6ffa3fd33bc936abb47690cd92.webm?t=1761030131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036940/extras/7f729f6ffa3fd33bc936abb47690cd92.mp4?t=1761030131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>黑暗的地点、神秘的声音和不可预测的威胁让你置身于未知卫星上的幽闭恐惧噩梦中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong></strong><strong> </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036940/extras/4fb16f8e2023ade1c841ccabf224a2f4.avif?t=1761030131\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036940/extras/25ea42786a8206a67ee1b9ee6c045497.poster.avif?t=1761030131\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036940/extras/25ea42786a8206a67ee1b9ee6c045497.webm?t=1761030131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036940/extras/25ea42786a8206a67ee1b9ee6c045497.mp4?t=1761030131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>面对多种敌人，从小型变种怪物到可怕的巨兽，它们将考验你的生存技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong> </strong>收集资源，升级装备，并发展技能以应对不断增加的挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036940/extras/02d77f136babfa7aa75a56c96e69446b.avif?t=1761030131\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找船员日志、之前任务的痕迹，发现坠毁的真正原因。还有其他人幸存下来吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><br>你的探险为何坠毁？是意外，还是有人故意将你置于死地？在塔尔沃斯上的每一步都让你接近真相——但问题是，你是否有足够的时间活着揭示它。</p>",
